Cell["\<\
In the thumbnail and the snapshots, the population data describe a bimodal \
distribution of serum glucose measurements in nondiabetic and diabetic \
populations [1].
This Demonstration is appropriate as an educational tool in medical \
statistics and diagnostic test evaluation.\
\>", "Text",
 Editable->False,
